   CCF Young Comp Sci \& Engn Forum Wuhan Branch; IEEE Ind Elect Soc; IEEE
   Ind Elect Soc Beijing Shenzhen Chapter},
Abstract = {A centralized management of metadata is essential for data warehouse
   administration, maintenance and usage. Typically, current systems only
   support some metadata types, it is difficult to define new metadata
   types in the repository, and interoperate on them properly. By analyzing
   the basic requirements and schema of metadata management, and discussing
   the functions of Meta Object Facility (MOF), a novel meta-model of
   metadata repository is proposed to support obtaining, administrating and
   presenting metadata, based on MOF. In prototype, the functionality with
   the object-relationship mapping model is implemented in the J2EE
   environment, based on a lightweight framework.},
