Abstract = {We introduce VTechData, a Sufia/Fedora based institutional repository
   specifically implemented to meet the needs of research data management
   at Virginia Tech. Despite the rapid maturity of Hydra and Fedora code
   bases, the gaps between the released packages and a launched
   production-level service are still many and far from trivial. In this
