Abstract = {Distance Learning is acquiring a role that becomes more and more
   important with the huge diffusion of the Internet and related
   technologies. Consequently, the investigation for adequate architectures
   and platforms supporting flexible Distance Learning engines and solution
   is nowadays of great interests in the Scientific Community. The present
   paper introduces a platform based on the adoption of Metadata concepts
   and on the use of a ``processor-like{''} behavior of the Web Course
   Delivery engine that appears to be a good solution when different and
   heterogeneous modules have to be integrated in the platform. The
   proposed system is currently under development and test in the framework
