Number = {2, SI},
Pages = {55-62},
Month = {MAR},
Abstract = {This paper describes a repository of openEHR archetypes that have been
   translated to OWL. In the work presented here, five different CKMs
   (Clinical Knowledge Managers) have been downloaded and the archetypes
   have been translated to OWL. This translation is based on an existing
   translator that has been improved to solve programming problems with
   certain structures. As part of the repository a tool has been developed
   to keep it always up-to-date. So, any change in one of the CKMs
   (addition, elimination or even change of an archetype) will involve
   translating the changed archetypes once more. The repository is
   accessible through a Web interface (http://www.openehr.es/).},
