   Chengdu, PEOPLES R CHINA, DEC 13-16, 2017},
Organization = {IEEE; Sichuan Inst Elect},
Abstract = {Because of the distributed nature of cloud computing, the data of cloud
   may be stored and processed across jurisdictional borders. In such case,
   collecting digital evidence from cloud computing requires multiparty
   cooperation. However, as far as we known, there is still no available
   technic approach for improving the trustworthy of the interaction
   records of all stakeholders in cloud forensics. This work proposed a
   process provenance, which provides proof of existence and privacy
   preservation for process records by using technologies of blockchain and
   cryptography group signature. The process provenance enhances the
   trustworthy of the chain of custody for cloud forensics.},
