Organization = {IEEE; IEEE Comp Soc},
Abstract = {Question repositories are organized collections of assessment questions
   (items) that serve many purposes. Questions required vary widely along
   many dimensions such as cognitive level, difficulty level content and
   question type depending upon the context in which it is used. This paper
   proposes a software system that semi-automatically generates metadata
   for items in a question repository. The metadata in this paper
   corresponds to ``cognitive level{''}, ``question type{''}, ``content{''}
   and ``difficulty level{''}. The developed system was tested for its
   usability and accuracy and the results are promising. The accuracy with
   respect to automatic generation of cognitive level tags was 78\% and
   other tags were generated with more than 90\% accuracy. Usability
   testing has shown that the system is user friendly and useful in
   multiple ways.},
